attributes.title: Ruined my phone

attributes.review:
So I downloaded this app hoping to see Mr.Trump in a different light. I also read all the reviews, most of them were poor, but I didn’t pay attention to those. I wanted to see what this app was with my own eyes. Needless to say, this app was straight up fire. 
   I was barbecue-ing in my oven like I usually do and I decided that now was the time to check out the app. ‘Cause you know, barbecues are one of Trumps favorite things to do, don’t ask how I know... 
   I unlocked my iPhone 3000 and had my griffin press the app for me because my hands were full tryna barbecue. I think it was right after my griffin pressed the app when it bursted into flames roasting my griffin into a chicken and blew up my phone. The explosion caused a domino effect and it exploded the oven I was barbecue-ing in, which in turn blew up my fridge, which was in my neighbors’ house, so my neighbors’ house blew up. My neighbors got so upset that they decided to rob everything in my house. I tried to stop them but I passed out due to all the stress. When I awoke I was on the sidewalk.. 
     I’m so upset right now because I lost everything because of this app! This is why I’m giving this app a one star. But thankfully my luck was finally turning around. I met Obama while I was crying in the streets and writing this review. He gave me a new place to stay, a new griffin, an iPhone 4000, and a new oven! I’m planning on deleting this app after writing a review and please warn people about how much of a fire hazard this app is. I hope you guys will fix this issue because it’s very dangerous, anyway thanks for coming to my TedTalk bye.^^
attributes.title: The app broke my oven and my iPhone 3000 and over-roasted my griffin. -n- I’m now homeless
